Binary Tree
    -> first node is -> root node
    -> node can have 2 children
    -> end notes -> leaf nodes
    -> level by level 1,2,3

    3 types of traversal
    -> preorder  ->  root, left, right
    -> inorder   ->  left, root, right
    -> postorder ->  left, right, root


